snippet.title: Hidden Pass Skirmishes. A mystical adventure in the fusion of Tactical Turn-Based RPG and Strategy
snippet.description: This is a small tactical adventure where you have to choose one of four groups of heroes and challenge three different groups of opponents. Starting with an easy group of enemies and ending with strong one.
